{"tid":718038,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"別了！謎一樣の昭和音樂真．女神 - 森田童子","createTime":"2018-06-26T13:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T12:10:06.000Z","uid":40662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f044caa8fb4a575df8f1d1ea6ccf5015e61ed327","tid":718038,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3bPd9Z7eqdw/WykoftmzQbI/AAAAAAAATqg/ZfvXfOwgcREWWo-_i1UQr-kxs4tEjnYAACLcBGAs/s1600/27ac9195ce4cb4105244fbeeaa333ecd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-3bPd9Z7eqdw%2FWykoftmzQbI%2FAAAAAAAATqg%2FZfvXfOwgcREWWo-_i1UQr-kxs4tEjnYAACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F27ac9195ce4cb4105244fbeeaa333ecd.jpg&h=a7943029&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n活躍於1970年代至1980年代初的日本傳奇唱作女歌手森田童子近日被證實於4月24日逝世，終年66歲。日本音樂著作權協會（JASRAC）於會報公佈她的死訊，雖然未有說明其死因，但有傳媒報道指森田是死於心臟衰竭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KHF5VHAmvNc/Wyktiu4nmsI/AAAAAAAATrU/mq4xEfEZrZgNobeoGSsNBUD_iFvnZAPvACLcBGAs/s1600/81f4e51bb7f2461eb29f8cb8686e786d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-KHF5VHAmvNc%2FWyktiu4nmsI%2FAAAAAAAATrU%2Fmq4xEfEZrZgNobeoGSsNBUD_iFvnZAPvACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F81f4e51bb7f2461eb29f8cb8686e786d.jpg&h=721d05b1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n森田童子於1972年因朋友逝世而開始音樂創作，並以細碟〈さよならぼくのともだち〉出道樂壇，然後於1976年她就憑著一曲〈ぼくたちの失敗〉正式走紅。森田為人非常低調，在入行以來身份一直成謎，從來沒有公開過自己的真實姓名，她整個音樂生涯主要都在一些Live House裡開騷，一生人就只曾推出過六張Studio Album和一張Live Album。 <br />\n<br />\n完整全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2018/06/Salute-To-Doji-Morita.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F06%2FSalute-To-Doji-Morita.html&d=aSudrojFQ0lCV3FZcZzkFbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=0f9b8053\" target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2018/06/Salute-To-Doji-Morita.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-co2kTIEG3cw/Wykv6ntT2MI/AAAAAAAATr4/vM7isAwCgBgXU_aY67icfeDpwPy9lHYeACLcBGAs/s1600/DSC_1095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-co2kTIEG3cw%2FWykv6ntT2MI%2FAAAAAAAATr4%2FvM7isAwCgBgXU_aY67icfeDpwPy9lHYeACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FDSC_1095.jpg&h=5e494e4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52c3e6142a9378e1519b2a593a38d6bc1ebd8af1","tid":718038,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-yI9rJkuNFNM/WykuRsA6voI/AAAAAAAATrc/8gvsJTywolwNDcWOob0EeZUi5GDUZRJrgCLcBGAs/s1600/DSC_1105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-yI9rJkuNFNM%2FWykuRsA6voI%2FAAAAAAAATrc%2F8gvsJTywolwNDcWOob0EeZUi5GDUZRJrgCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FDSC_1105.jpg&h=52678b74&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長文裡面會詳細介紹一下森田童子歷年嚟嘅一啲好歌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0cef2ef62770a9a7c57e6673625522a1dda2db","tid":718038,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e454cfdef1ba8aad9261bbe8862494368e2c58cb","tid":718038,"uid":50006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"dc8bf2a611c99ec3d328c8767d6d8af44745931e","tid":718038,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c4fc14a748ae744f22eca319dd7931c686884b","tid":718038,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bd01445c49bfed710a63f9a73368b3622f9f53","tid":718038,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c